text: Doug Bohaboy (born 25 September 1976) is a retired American tennis player. Bohaboy has a career high ATP singles ranking of 250 achieved on 23 June 2003. He also has a career high doubles ranking of 222 achieved on 23 September 2002. Bohaboy has won 1 ATP Challenger doubles title at the 2002 Tampere Open. ==Tour titles== {| class=wikitable !
